On the other hand, Wildcard has struggled with consistency, particularly highlighted by their elimination at the hands of BIG and Spirit in recent tournaments. Given the recent form and roster stability, OG seems to have an edge. The map picks are likely to exclude Mirage and Train due to Wildcard's low win rate on Mirage and both teams rarely picking Train. OG might ban Dust2 due to their struggles on it, and Wildcard could ban Nuke given their poor performance on this map.
